{"tid":744002,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)深海狂鯊","createTime":"2018-07-15T17:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T18:27:08.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3364bf18970fc5324af0ea3f0fce2966d646b5e3","tid":744002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=efbce24d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7983afd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=14b8b449\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/73/Deep_Blue_Sea_(1999_film)_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F73%2FDeep_Blue_Sea_%281999_film%29_poster.jpg&h=fc862430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基因遺傳學家蘇珊博士所領導的研究小組，想要探索可以改變物種的基因，他們在位於海洋的實驗室做研究，她以聰明而且有攻擊力、生命力都很強的殺人鯨作為改造基因的實驗對象，他們發現從這種魚腦中所萃取的酵素可以治療腦癌。<br />\n<br />\n這項發現讓出資的金主羅素等人，在墨西哥海岸砸錢養鯊魚。他們需要腦容量大的鯊魚，可是這些鯊魚也是比較聰明的魚類。其中羅素是個神經質的人，他覺得這種基因實驗的本質違背自然運行之理，會遭到報應.......<br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a6daf41\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bc54d5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656f4b085694d8db28480352cacc71118680f1e0","tid":744002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc84205c854d4191c3cdb128d40210e8092c00ac","tid":744002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372fd7b52e4cdcc6562a2a48e7d8e0c74a1c2790","tid":744002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}